            <span style="font-weight: 800; font-size: 0.85rem; color: #ffffff; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.35rem;"><i class="fas fa-gas-pump" style="color: var(--color-accent);"></i> HIRE7 MOBILE</span>
